Townhouse in gated community with excellent location, walking distance to HEB Plus, Doctors Hospital, Restaurants, Gym and direct access to North Central Park. Available September 15, 2021.

Renter responsible for all utilities.
Assigned covered parking for two vehicles.
Home Owners Association rules apply.
Community pool for owners/tenants use.
No Pets.
